## Local overrides

If you need to add instructions specific to your local checkout (not committed), put them in `<root>/dev/CLAUDE.local.md`. That file is `.gitignore`d and is read by Claude Code automatically; for Codex compatibility, ALSO copy the same content into `<root>/dev/AGENTS.local.md` (also gitignored).
